snippet.title: Brominion Preview Gameplay
snippet.description:
Brominion is a fantasy battler game that's fully integrated with Twitch! Your viewers can participate and build their armies to duel other players, or fight monsters. Brominion serve to provide an additional interactivity for your Twitch livestream :)

Wishlist Brominion on steam today!
